Package com.mydogspies.xflymetar.apis

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    APIDataIO
    This interface is the endpoint for the API logic and should be implemented by the API handler.
    DataObserverIO
    This interface is an integral part of the observer network.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APIData
    This class uses Retrofit and the Simple XML serialization network in order to grab Metar, Taf and Airport data.
    APIDataSingleton
    This class is the single only reference to the API data handler.
    PojoAirport
    The Retrofit Pojo for the airport data from api.flightplandatabase.com The string dataType denotes which API we got data from.

    PojoAirport.Navaids  
    PojoAirport.Runway  
    PojoAirport.Times  
    PojoAirport.Timezone  
    PojoMetar
    The Retrofit Pojo for the METAR data from aviationweather.gov.
    PojoTaf
    The Retrofit Pojo for the TAF data from aviationweather.gov.
    PojoTaf.Forecast
